22T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"略.....？"},{"pid":"df6bbb916e2b317cc1306f94d5462befc00639da","tid":911693,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"真識食"},{"pid":"e64d86037dddcad7d3477676a06b4f252a623255","tid":911693,"uid":55194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"柒到盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d205250bbc94a046d0000d86462b6607db26df1","tid":911693,"uid":28870,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"樣衰唔係罪，係不幸。生得醜唔係你嘅責任，要怪嘅，只好怪上帝<br />\n但係，肥，就係你嘅錯！ 一個人好地地係唔會肥嘅，你變得做肥人，梗係食咗多過你需要嘅嘢啦 喺呢個仲有咁多人捱餓嘅時代，你竟然食咁多嘢？ 肥係貪心嘅表現，係唔公平嘅象徵 肥人臃腫畸形嘅身體，已經充分顯示出佢哋嘅唔道德<br />\n<br />\n肥人係罪犯，佢哋甚至比小偷、殺人犯更無恥 一般犯人都會掩飾自己犯咗嘅罪 但係肥人，佢哋竟然將自己嘅罪證放晒響個身上，就好似一個殺人犯拖住條屍周街走咁 你話，見到肥人有乜辦法唔憤怒？<br />\n<br />\n所以，見到肥人應該即刻鬧佢，就算唔鬧佢都要鄙視佢，我哋要透過侮辱嚟喚醒佢嘅良知 喺街見到肥人唔鬧佢，就好似搭地鐵見到痴漢非禮學生妹唔出聲一樣 作為一個有良知嘅人，我哋應該出聲，應該鼓起勇氣挺身而出鬧到佢哋狗血淋頭！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6353d8f785b8da41f676061ad5e84e00fb392a69","tid":911693,"uid":15538,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:10:38.000Z","msg":"明眼人一睇就知男事主係世外高人<br />\n你以為佢醉？ <br />\n少年，你太年輕喇。<br />\n男事主不知幾清醒，甚至比大家都清醒。<br />\n作為一個看破紅塵嘅高人，抱住「我不入地獄，誰入地獄」，冒住千夫所指嘅危險去拯救一隻豬。 <br />\n豬，係豬呀！ 就好似唐三藏對豬八戒咁呀屌你個閪！<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係打算派錢畀一隻豬纖體整容，而係打算捨身取義，捐精救人呀！<br />\n<br />\n一隻豬都有尊嚴。<br />\n如果呢隻豬一個睇唔開，走去跳樓，可能會壓死人、壓爛坦克車、甚至深陷地核，電腦大爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n只有奶乾淨佢「三字」肚腩嘅千年老泥，再大大力屌到自己盤骨骨碎裂，先可以阻止呢場災難。 <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，男事主需要大家支持。<br />\n<br />\n重有，一支美極。"},{"pid":"1932b7b012e19f9376e331b1e6a6676462ca2263","tid":911693,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef18450dd6fb99a30104529df4f61e33fe6a1e0","tid":911693,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"個男人真係醉得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a906cb27205f6d7cd002ff62a42422c370532cf2","tid":911693,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de11e819eb9381d9a8fd2b49a443bf64315e22b1","tid":911693,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dceec65d0577f2031106acaac332443c7294fb8","tid":911693,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"非洲饑民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d86d225a876d5d064639d8ea05c5a185249c2b","tid":911693,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee64f85e555bdee4e0f32a0e5e90f4a54c2bb219","tid":911693,"uid":220431,"like":855,"dislike":2,"score":853,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:53:54.000Z","msg":"一名身材略胖姓張(23歲)女子搭訕<br />\n<br />\n咁撚賤既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"寫做一名姓張23歲女子(略胖)會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed24401a516b024824ef871402c4dc81831a758","tid":911693,"uid":47320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"個男既醒咗心諗:好彩唔成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog